// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5469 — Mass File Rename (medusa)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2ccf3d4d-a058-5388-8af5-5202b27aae8f

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
